{"title":"痛悼小平同志","authors":["洪学智"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛悼小平同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪学智"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赖有伟人运幄帷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨星陨落共一悲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音容笑貌今犹在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟绩丰功口皆碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南针路线指航向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北辰思想放光辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三代核心承遗志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千秋大业永腾飞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}